{"type": "article", "id": 22817, "title": "混凝土风景物件", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071222021EnGMHQKYm7ivSLc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套放首饰的混凝土容器，是通过 3D 打印完成的。它的每一款造型都有据可循，将世界上知名的山脉按原比例缩小的，有 5 个连绵山脉的是北美的大提顿山脉，带有缺口的是夏威夷哈利阿卡拉火山。硬币、首饰之类的金属在原始混凝土的反衬下色泽更亮，也能突出这种人工的精巧。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122200t0farFs8B6Nl9XLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122201IZo204iSgDQY5dml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89119804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122201BCz4hIkbWKN7HlcU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122202QtNluZvaJrIR0ihB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><br></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}